casebandit-verify
Copyright 2026 CaseBandit

This product includes algorithm leaves vendored verbatim (content-hash-pinned)
from the CaseBandit application source. See README.md "Vendored-leaf content-hash
pins". The vendored leaves are the forensic chain-tip composition, canonical
ledger sort, RFC 3161 messageImprint containment check, the JCS RFC 8785
canonicalizer, and the row-HMAC message builder.

This product depends on tweetnacl (https://github.com/dchest/tweetnacl-js),
which is released into the public domain.
